---
title: Fire-Blasted Vegan Coconut Curry Soup with Chickpeas, Cauliflower & Toast
description: When the chips are down, Rocket always comes through. And, like our fuzzy pal, you’ll come through for your family (or chosen family!) by cheffin’ up this galaxy-approved meal. You’ll simmer up a powerful combo of coconut milk, cauliflower florets, chickpeas, and flavor-blasted spices to evoke the complexity, warmth, and spiciness of Rocket. Plus there’s crispy ciabatta toasts for dunking and crunching. Do you have what it takes to cook like a hero?
